name: Unnatural (itch) (BenBabicka)
description:
An escape room-type game, find out what is going on in this unnatural place. Complete puzzles to allow yourself to escape. Is this a real place?

Controls: 

(W,S,A,D) to move around

(E) to interact

This game was created for the Brackeys Game Jam 2022.1

Credits:

Created by Ben Babicka
